@startuml
title 可配置订单流程引擎执行时序（以实物订单为例）

actor "买家" as buyer
participant "IGW Buyer" as gw
participant "workflow-service" as wf
participant "ProcessEngine" as engine
participant "ProcessTemplateRepo" as repo
participant "OrderClassifier" as classifier
participant "StrategyRegistry" as sr
participant "HookDispatcher" as hd
participant "SagaExecutor" as saga
database "Apollo" as apollo
database "SagaLog DB" as slog

== 1. 订单提交 ==

buyer -> gw: POST /api/v1/orders (商品 SKU + 购买属性)
gw -> wf: 路由到 workflow-service
wf -> engine: process(orderRequest)

== 2. 订单分类 ==

engine -> classifier: classify(orderRequest)
activate classifier

classifier -> classifier: 提取商品属性\n(itemType, saleType, bizAttributes)
classifier -> apollo: 从 Apollo 加载分类规则\n(process.category)
apollo --> classifier: 规则列表（SpEL 表达式）
classifier -> classifier: 按顺序匹配规则\nPHYSICAL_GOODS+NORMAL → "physical"
classifier --> engine: OrderCategory.physical
deactivate classifier

== 3. 模板加载 ==

engine -> repo: getTemplate("physical_flow")
activate repo

repo -> apollo: 从 Apollo 加载模板 YAML\n(process.template)
apollo --> repo: physical_flow YAML 定义
repo -> repo: YAML 解析为\nProcessTemplate 对象
repo --> engine: ProcessTemplate
deactivate repo

note right of engine
  模板包含:
  - 7 个步骤定义
  - 4 个策略配置
  - 2 个 Hook 事件
end note

== 4. 策略绑定 ==

engine -> sr: resolve(physical, template.strategies)
activate sr

sr -> apollo: 从 Apollo 加载策略映射\n(如 split→by_warehouse)
apollo --> sr: 策略实现 Bean 名
sr -> sr: 从 Spring 容器获取\n策略实现实例
sr --> engine: ProcessStrategies
deactivate sr

note right of engine
  当前策略:
  split=by_warehouse
  merge=by_vendor
  shipping=by_weight
  invoice=by_amount
end note

== 5. 构建 Saga 定义 ==

engine -> engine: buildSagaDefinition(template, strategies, hooks)
note right of engine
  步骤 0: resolveSplitStrategy(策略步骤)
  步骤 1: validate
  步骤 2: calculatePrice
  步骤 3: applyPromotion
  步骤 4: applyCoupon
  步骤 5: reserveInventory
  步骤 6: createOrder
  步骤 7: requestPayment
  Hook: after_payment → async
  Hook: after_complete → async
end note

== 6. 执行 Saga ==

engine -> saga: execute(sagaDefinition, context)
activate saga

saga -> slog: 创建 saga_instance (INITIATED)
slog --> saga: saga_id

== 7. 正向步骤执行 ==

saga -> saga: step[0] resolveSplitStrategy
saga -> saga: 执行拆单策略\n(by_warehouse → 拆为 2 组)
note right of saga
  拆单结果：
  组1: warehouse_1 (3 件商品)
  组2: warehouse_2 (1 件商品)
end note

saga -> saga: 为每组执行子流程

loop 每组
    saga -> saga: step[1] validate (OK)
    saga -> saga: step[2] calculatePrice (含运费计算)
    note right of saga
      ShippingCostStrategy:
      by_weight 计算运费
    end note

    saga -> saga: step[3] applyPromotion
    saga -> saga: step[4] applyCoupon
    saga -> saga: step[5] reserveInventory
    saga -> saga: step[6] createOrder
    saga -> saga: step[7] requestPayment

    saga -> slog: 更新 step_log (SUCCESS)
end

saga -> slog: 更新 saga_instance (COMPLETED || PAID)

== 8. 扩展点触发 ==

alt after_payment Hook
    saga -> hd: dispatch("after_payment", hookContext)
    activate hd

    hd -> hd: pointsGrantHandler(order:1, async)
    note right of hd
      条件: totalAmount >= 100
      当前金额 299 → 满足 → 执行
    end note

    group 异步 MQ
        hd -> hd: pointsGrantHandler\n发送积分赠送 MQ 消息
        hd -> hd: firstOrderCouponIssuer(异步)\n如果是首单 → 发放优惠券
    end

    hd --> saga: Hook 调度完成
    deactivate hd
end

alt after_complete Hook
    saga -> hd: dispatch("after_complete", hookContext)
    activate hd
    hd -> hd: crmSyncHandler(异步)
    hd --> saga: Hook 调度完成
    deactivate hd
end

== 9. 返回结果 ==

saga --> engine: SagaResult.success(orderNo)
engine --> wf: OrderProcessResult
wf --> gw: HTTP 201 (订单创建成功)
gw --> buyer: 响应订单信息

@enduml
